item.title: AntaresBox

item.description:
Our classic AntaresBox model rocket. Learn and discover the world of science behind rockets, all while having fun with this product for all ages.

The post AntaresBox appeared first on Åntares.
item.content:encoded:
Our classic AntaresBox model rocket is a modern rendition of the old rocket models, made not only for Launchig, but for learning along the way, and building something for yourself.

It includes:

  • 2x Structure frames
  • 1x Nosecone
  •  4x Fins
  • 1x Fincan
  • 4x Reflective stickers
  • 1x Parachute
  • 3x C5 Engines
